<subSubSection id="B262AA5E452BEE93745CBBC4A1A6C528" pageId="0" pageNumber="347" type="remarks">
<paragraph id="D9E40800BBC57218490E22B362026E0E" pageId="0" pageNumber="347">Remark.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="55E092E7FB459C45FB345AC63F13362E" pageId="0" pageNumber="347">
We have not reexamined the holotype of 
<taxonomicName id="388C4D651CD5266875B7FF2600AEAA11" family="Halictidae" genus="S." kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="S. campadellii" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="347" rank="species" species="campadellii">
<emphasis id="DA3A58E4B2BD2392AC67E14D68ACDFF7" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="347">S. campadellii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
because it has not been found in IUB/ ZSM and probably is lost. However, we agree with its synonymy with 
<taxonomicName id="6924577D909BAA0A87EEDBE47AB1BA2D" family="Halictidae" genus="S." kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="S. geoffrellus" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="347" rank="species" species="geoffrellus">
<emphasis id="E6DDC8A7ABB6D3E4EA7ED39D632C3F64" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="347">S. geoffrellus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as previously suggested by 
<bibRefCitation id="AEC946B381CE7DC6C84E6E9CA6D78B1A" author="Schwarz, M" journalOrPublisher="Entomofauna" pageId="0" pageNumber="347" pagination="73 - 80" refId="B10" refString="Schwarz, M, Gusenleitner, F, 2012. Zur Kenntnis der von Nobile V. &amp; G.F. Turrisi (2004) aus Italien beschriebenen Sphecodes -Arten (Hymenoptera, Apidae). Entomofauna 33: 73 - 80" title="Zur Kenntnis der von Nobile V. &amp; G. F. Turrisi (2004) aus Italien beschriebenen Sphecodes - Arten (Hymenoptera, Apidae)." volume="33" year="2012">Schwarz and Gusenleitner (2012)</bibRefCitation>
based on type studies.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
